Ok so you  all may or may not be familiar with the number game, but basically you post a picture with a number in it in sequence. 1, 2, 3 etc... and so on. It can either be a picture with a number in the picture, a length of a fish, number of fish, weight of a fish on a scale, etc....  size of a motor, length of a boat, anything fishing related get ready to get creative with the higher numbers. If there is a double post or out of sync you the first wins and you need to edit it out. Self policing, keep it fun and good luck, lets see them fish pictures.  I'll start with  1 crappie
